data.description: A charming single family residence in a quiet cul-de-sac neighborhood, this delightful 4 bedrooms, 2 baths is now available, offers a comfortable and spacious living experience. Build in 1995, well maintained home boasts a generous 2003 sq ft of living space. The interior formal living room with a beautiful brick fireplace, a great room with vaulted ceilings and bay windows. Enjoy the adjacent stunning kitchen with porcelain counter top with tile backsplash, stainless appliances, farmhouse kitchen sink, and a range/oven. This property also include two car garage with the drive thru garage giving extra room to store or work in your vehicles, covered patio for outdoor entertainment. This property is located in the North West of Bakersfield in the desirable Rosedale Schools. With a walk distance parks. Make appointment to view this property.
